{Name}{}{Ghost}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see a Ghost.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see a Ghost looking like good old Jippers Krippers.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see a Ghost. He is really scary!.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see a Ghost. You don't believe in supernaturals, but you believe your eyes.}
{Speech 1}{}{Initial preferences}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{-}
{Speech 2}{}{[You see a ghost. His face is covered in blood. Clothes soiled all over with blood and slime. He has a terrible smell that you felt long before you came here]}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{I know all about you, prepare to die!}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{What evil spirit is this?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Motherfucker! Let’s get the hell out of here! [You run away cowardly]}
{Speech 3}{}{[It looks like the ghost is happy to see his prey. He cries stridently and dashes over you. You dodged barely but the ghost continues his assault]}
{Speech 3 Answer 4}{}{[Attack him]}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Hell with ya! I will come back.}
{Speech 4}{}{Aarrgghh!}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{[You take the flask with Holy Water and sprinkle the ghost with it]}
{Speech 4 Answer 5}{}{[You punch and kick him with all your might, trying to do as much damage as possible]}
{Speech 4 Answer 5*}{}{[You lean on him heavily with your body, ripping great pieces of his flesh with your teeth]}
{Speech 4 Answer 5**}{}{[Apply all the hand weapons you are carrying]}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit*}{}{[It looks like your attacks don't hurt him. You should ask around before you try again]}
{Speech 5}{}{[He cries when you hit him but it doesn’t seem to give any physical damage whatsoever]}
{Speech 5 Answer 4}{}{[Try one more time]}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{Fuck it!}
{100000001}{}{Aarrgghh!}
{100000002}{}{You feel that you just took a handfull of hot rocks. You shake your hand violently, trying to get rid of burning sensation. Small burns are left all over your hands to remind you of this incident.}
{100000003}{}{You feel like you just grabbed a handfull of lava. Your hand began to burn and terrible smell of burned flash appearad in the air. You shake your hand violently, trying to shake it off, to save at least a bit of your hand. After the pain settles you realise that your hand was a terribe mess of burned flesh and coals.}
